SQL_STMT_U.val: select LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_LDGR_NO, cast(sum(LGCC_AMOUNTH) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/LGCC inner join :1/LDGR on LDGR_ADMNO = LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO and LDGR_NO = LGCC_LDGR_NO and LDGR_PRINTONMONTHLYINVOICE = 'Y' where LGCC_ACCC_ACCT_DATE between ':2' and ':3' :4 :5 and LGCC_AMOUNTH <> 0 and (LGCC_OMITONMONTHLYINVOICE = 'N' or LGCC_OMITONMONTHLYINVOICE = '' or LGCC_OMITONMONTHLYINVOICE is null) group by LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_LDGR_NO order by LGCC_LGCD_ADMNO, LGCC_LDGR_NO for fetch only
